comments: Johnson (SAS) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Branham (SAS) and Prince (LAL) mutually engage and marginal contact occurs as they jostle for rebounding position.
Davis (LAL) contests Wembanyama's (SAS) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Wembanyama (SAS) legally contests Davis' (LAL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Davis (LAL) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Johnson (SAS) during the steal attempt.
Vassell (SAS) immediately slides his hand off Davis' (LAL) body and marginal contact occurs as the errant pass bounces away from Davis.
Reaves (LAL) avoids contact with Branham (SAS) during his contest on the play at the basket.
Russell (LAL) establishes position in the frontcourt prior to receiving the pass from Reaves (LAL).
Vassell (SAS) avoids making contact with Reaves' (LAL) arm during his contest on the jump shot attempt.
Wood (LAL) extends his forearm and initiates contact with Wembanyama's (SAS) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Russell (LAL) establishes himself in Wembanyama's (SAS) path and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during the screen.
Wembanyama (SAS) reaches for the ball and makes illegal contact with Davis' (LAL) face.

Replay review of the foul called on Wembanyama (SAS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Wembanyama overtly extends his leg out to make more than marginal contact with Reddish (LAL) after the release on his jump shot attempt. Subsequently, the game clock is reset to 00:10.9.

After Branham (SAS) cleanly deflects the inbound pass, Prince (LAL) runs alongside Branham in pursuit of the loose ball and slightly extends his forearm as marginal contact occurs while Prince stumbles to the ground.
Branham (SAS) steps out of bounds while in possession of the ball.
Johnson (SAS) reaches for the ball and initiates illegal contact with Davis' (LAL) shoulder as he receives the inbound pass.
Prince (LAL) legally contests Branham's (SAS) jump shot attempt.
Branham (SAS) commits a take foul on Prince (LAL).
Prince (LAL) turns to pursue the full court pass and marginal contact occurs when he comes together with Sochan (SAS) as the errant pass sails over their heads.
